<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="priorProvisions" id="idbc95fc83-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Prior Provisions</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">A prior <ref href="/us/pl/90/284/s819">section 819 of Pub. L. 90–284</ref> was renumbered section 820 and is classified to <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s3619">section 3619 of this title</ref>.</p>
